    "body": "Hey @ta99i, your config should be something like this:\r\n\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  solidity: {\r\n    version: \"0.8.17\",\r\n    settings: {\r\n      optimizer: {\r\n        enabled: true,\r\n        runs: 1000,\r\n      },\r\n      viaIR: true,\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe `solidity: \"0.8.17\"` shortcut is only used when you want to use the default settings.",
